headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Earn Your Wings and Extra Rewards with Flight-Themed Bonuses
content:
Airborne vehicles and activities take center stage this week. Gear up for success in Flight School, protect yourself against above-ground attacks in Stockpile and Air Quota, and stick the landing in Junk Energy Skydives for a host of pulse-pounding adrenaline highs.

Plus, compete in high-altitude Freemode Events and Challenges for double GTA$ and RP, get 20% off Hangar properties, and more all week long.
